### Arabic

<span style="display: block; font-size: 180%; text-align: right;">لَا تَعْتَذِرُوا۟ قَدْ كَفَرْتُم بَعْدَ إِيمَـٰنِكُمْ ۚ إِن نَّعْفُ عَن طَآئِفَةٍ مِّنكُمْ نُعَذِّبْ طَآئِفَةًۢ بِأَنَّهُمْ كَانُوا۟ مُجْرِمِينَ</span>

### English

Make no excuses! You have lost faith after your belief. If We pardon a group of you, We will punish others for their wickedness.